 action for a specific Form.\n</ol>\n<h2>Use-cases</h2>\n<ol>\n- Let your user contact with you for a good or services you are providing.\n- Let users give you feedback for the post they are reading.\n</ol>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:43:\"Let your users contact the author of a Post\";s:10:\"banner_url\";s:61:\"//s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/freemius/plugins/5721/banner.png\";s:15:\"card_banner_url\";s:66:\"//s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/freemius/plugins/5721/card_banner.png\";s:15:\"selling_point_0\";s:28:\"Contact the author of a Post\";s:15:\"selling_point_1\";s:71:\"Let your user contact with you for a good or services you are providing\";s:15:\"selling_point_2\";s:57:\"Let users give you feedback for the post they are reading\";s:11:\"screenshots\";N;s:2:\"id\";s:4:\"1492\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2020-03-15 00:09:22\";s:7:\"updated\";s:19:\"2020-04-08 22:32:27\";}s:12:\"premium_slug\";s:33:\"buddyforms-contact-author-premium\";}}}s:7:\"created\";i:1587312223;s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1587398623;}s:46:\"get:/v1/users/251593/licenses.json?type=active\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:6:\"result\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"licenses\";a:23:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:9:\"plugin_id\";s:4:\"5792\";s:7:\"user_id\";s:6:\"251593\";s:7:\"plan_id\";s:4:\"9466\";s:10:\"pricing_id\";s:4:\"9414\";s:5:\"quota\";i:6;s:9:\"activated\";i:1;s:15:\"activated_local\";i:1;s:10:\"expiration\";s:19:\"2021-03-26 15:37:06\";s:10:\"secret_key\";s:32:\"sk_qdxzKMwMNC)qbly&8[4&q*~:8UAmc\";s:17:\"is_free_localhost\";b:1;s:17:\"is_block_features\";b:0;s:12:\"is_cancelled\";b:0;s:15:\"is_whitelabeled\";b:0;s:11:\"environment\";i:0;s:6:\"source\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"317269\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2020-03-26 15:37:06\";s:7:\"updated\";s:19:\"2020-03-27 19:51:26\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:9:\"plugin_id\";s:4:\"5793\";s:7:\"user_id\";s:6:\"251593\";s:7:\"plan_id\";s:4:\"9468\";s:10:\"pricing_id\";s:4:\"9416\";s:5:\"quota\";i:6;s:9:\"activated\";i:0;s:15:\"activated_local\";i:1;s:10:\"expiration\";s:19:\"2021-